{"n":104,"name":"الهمزة","phonetic":"Al-Humazah","fr":"Les calomniateurs","type":"meccan","verses":[["وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","Malheur à tout calomniateur diffamateur","Waylun likulli humazatin lumazatin"],["ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","qui amasse une fortune et la compte","Allathee jamaAAa malan waAAaddadahu"],["يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","pensant que sa fortune l'immortalisera","Yahsabu anna malahu akhladahu"],["كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","Mais non! Il sera certes, jeté dans la Hutamah","Kalla layunbathanna fee alhutamati"],["وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحُطَمَةُ","Et qui te dira ce qu'est la Hutamah","Wama adraka ma alhutamatu"],["نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُوقَدَةُ","Le Feu attisé d'Allah","Naru Allahi almooqadatu"],["ٱلَّتِي تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلۡأَفۡـِٔدَةِ","qui monte jusqu'aux cœurs","Allatee tattaliAAu AAala alafidati"],["إِنَّهَا عَلَيۡهِم مُّؤۡصَدَةٞ","Il se refermera sur eux","lnnaha AAalayhim musadatun"],["فِي عَمَدٖ مُّمَدَّدَةِۭ","en colonnes (de flammes) étendues","Fee AAamadin mumaddadatin"]]}